articles.title: MotoGP 2023’s unluckiest rider just had his weirdest DNF yet - The Race
articles.description: Miguel Oliveira recorded another 2023 MotoGP retirement at the Austrian GP, but his fifth Sunday DNF this season was his strangest yet.
articles.content:
Miguel Oliveira’s early exit from the Austrian Grand Prix on Sunday was his fifth retirement from eight 2023 starts – and arguably the oddest of the MotoGP season so far.
